              "text": "Blowing saints away from Christ who is the Head,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Building not the Body, tearing down instead."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thus we must relinquish doctrines of all kinds,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Only keep the faith that oneness we may find."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In the Lord the Spirit we are one indeed;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Just to keep this oneness is our only need."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Truth we must be holding, which is Christ Himself,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That we be delivered from the sects of self,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That in all things growing into Christ the Head,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Built will be the Body and to fulness led."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To the “unity of faith” we must attain,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All the “winds of doctrine” evermore disdain;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Holding Christ the Spirit, our reality,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For the Body’s growing in its unity."
            }
          ]
        }
